   Jobs
   How to apply

   Current Bechtel BWXT Idaho, LLC Employees:
   Request for Internal Promotion and/or Transfer (form 323.01) MUST be
   attached to the e-mail submitted for consideration. A copy of this form
   can be found in the Lotus Notes Forms Index under Human Resources,
   Employment. All other applicants:
   E-mail is our preference for submitting a resume, since it enables us
   to get your resume to the hiring manager faster.
   1) Locate the desired job description on the main Jobs page (click on
   "View Job Postings").
   2) Click on the Reference Number. An email page will open.
   3) Send an email note and attach your resume. If you do not have email,
   please mail or fax your resume to the address below with a cover letter
   containing the reference number of the job posting.
   Staffing
   Bechtel BWXT Idaho, LLC
   P. O. Box 1625
   Idaho Falls, ID 83415-3127
   Our fax number is: (208) 526-0025
   Page contact: jzg@inel.gov.

